{"tid":849629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家)「砍腳趾避沙蟲？」為控制強奸案件的上升 xx政府發禁令關閉所有色情網站!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-10-05T22:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T23:04:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b15722aa616ec674b5a5e657335dc33ed49dea4","tid":849629,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T22:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.techapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/387103-symbolicpornpic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F387103-symbolicpornpic.jpg&h=31bdd042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾政府上個月向所有互聯網服務提供商發佈禁令，通知所有互聯網服務提供商（ISP）禁閉國內的色情網站，旨在控制強奸案件數量上升的措施。<br />\n<br />\n通告內容：<br />\n<br />\n根提「刑法典」的第2071條第121條和其他普遍法律禁止製作和傳播淫穢內容。為了防止通過電子媒體訪問此類內容，有必要在尼泊爾內部刪除此類網站。<br />\n<br />\n日前，尼泊爾國家電信協會（NTA）的發言人表示，色情內容已經成為該國社會文化方面的威脅，因為即使是青少年兒童也會對色情內容上癮。尼泊爾政府此舉，令一些互聯網服務提供商感到了擔憂，因為每天都會出現新的色情網站，很難在色情網站上留下標籤。此外，被一個ISP阻止的網站可能不會被另一個ISP阻止。據報導，一些互聯網服務提供商已經阻止了部分色情網站。<br />\n<br />\n這已經不是尼泊爾當局第一次禁止色情內容。 在2010年，政府禁止在其內容中包含「性」的一些網站，但效果並不高。而尼泊爾的鄰居，印度也進行了各種限制色情活動的嘗試。 印度在2015年，下令ISP禁止857個網站，但最終事與願遺。<br />\n<br />\n不過，單單是關閉色情網站就能夠限制強奸案件的發生嗎？做好教育和立法懲罰罪犯才能做到良性的帶頭作用吧！"},{"pid":"ca0a9d28b6d985ce88d3fd24a159faf81f30eeca","tid":849629,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T22:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.techapple.com/archives/26001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techapple.com%2Farchives%2F26001&d=Kxubg5lyxominCtMoJIXmZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=b46e75b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techapple.com/archives/26001</a>"},{"pid":"00fb2d247d1b002d4b84cf21528f9e02d6bdb241","tid":849629,"uid":103887,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T22:40:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4df594af830960976d4969e9512aec00b1d69064","tid":849629,"uid":166413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T22:42:57.000Z","msg":"南亞撚連飛機都冇得打性慾仲勁，仲多強姦"},{"pid":"f325979a6804f4bf09f8c4fc6c8b9d7a99f637e7","tid":849629,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9131636636c3ce2075f880d5d56ba2b59334af5a","tid":849629,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"閹哂d男人佢治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9ceda63e66f56ad486d89a3285ba0e492f50ed","tid":849629,"uid":199331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:03:28.000Z","msg":"咁做會唔會迫少數睇av打飛機洩慾嘅良民走去老強？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3474b7359584534b18a71b7cc761004c02e1ed3d","tid":849629,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:04:09.000Z","msg":"強奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48dbe257a9679c7dee31777b2174a1abaf5d78e","tid":849629,"uid":58054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd9ceda63e66f56ad486d89a3285ba0e492f50ed","tid":849629,"uid":199331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:03:28.000Z","msg":"咁做會唔會迫少數睇av打飛機洩慾嘅良民走去老強？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係捉晒啲老鼠,就可以餓死晒啲蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}